    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>由于最近用<a href="https://www.vmware.com/cn/products/workstation-pro/workstation-pro-evaluation.html">vmware</a>编译openwrt,导致单个虚拟磁盘文件过大，准备分开存储Linux系统文件和openwrt编译文件。</p><h2 id="初步准备"><a href="#初步准备" class="headerlink" title="初步准备"></a>初步准备</h2><h3 id="1-先用df命令产看当前已挂载的磁盘"><a href="#1-先用df命令产看当前已挂载的磁盘" class="headerlink" title="1.先用df命令产看当前已挂载的磁盘"></a>1.先用df命令产看当前已挂载的磁盘</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">df</span> -h</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/.com//pic1.png"></p><h3 id="2-使用fdisk命令查看所有分区"><a href="#2-使用fdisk命令查看所有分区" class="headerlink" title="2.使用fdisk命令查看所有分区"></a>2.使用fdisk命令查看所有分区</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">~$ sudo fdisk -l</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/.com//pic1.png"></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
